RG777QVBz2UBT65Kq3NI3_kOd0NCt5Ise9ouA&oe=67656BC1"}, {"file_name": "Meta1.png", "id": "1664059377743239", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001662_1664059381076572_2784073303393704421_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=DZlFl7DFaMUQ7kNvgEbTEU2&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAkdkGwCuEF4D0kq8fRaXgLcRLgXjaquPXvRll0xXs_Hw&oe=6765570E"}, {"file_name": "Meta6.png", "id": "7549278421773967", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035372_7549278431773966_2638085679670106173_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Ks67oKBJYF0Q7kNvgEgog8A&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDQKyUcKaSxU2-Ci8nHdkwHhMCyz8WhPeRMiM42xTkxiA&oe=676557E0"}, {"file_name": "Meta12.png", "id": "857837239721372", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974598_857837243054705_1586444282118734467_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=dsmX_xnK5eAQ7kNvgHDUEuZ&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBW_mBiiUu4i46TXzCixEmrhpTiaC_6JJ5bGvMmUdMGHw&oe=67655CE9"}, {"file_name": "Meta7.png", "id": "2165357833831784", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974715_2165357837165117_6045858374784055506_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2BsAAyxqYZMQ7kNvgHvE6_n&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBJloiY5wqUX2BKbSxmTrKrAN_YmrDKuGBb6Nocx_u8yA&oe=67655E00"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Cover-Landscape-WithoutLogo.png", "id": "1277941789567918", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57570298_1277941792901251_4327650240598959447_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1ZhZPqGpkf4Q7kNvgHZVukW&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBDirrBXbn9UlI_vHLC2CZZgm1RVVMsVwE1r5s9eNxFZQ&oe=67656F39"}, "display_name": "Astro Hunters VR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "THE HUNT BEGINS\n\nBecome one of the mercenaries called Hunters and help the Mothership achieve its objectives on the hostile planets. Undertake dangerous missions and challenge other players and in exchange freely scavenge the planets. You can join forces with other players, but be careful, hunting down other players to seize their valuable equipment is also an option! Going on an expedition comes with a high reward if you find valuable items, but it\u2019s also high risk - if you die, you lose everything!\n\n{829898259015920}\n\nGATHER RESOURCES AND CRAFT\n\nCollect resources such as gases, liquids, metals and others on different planets. Each of the resources has its special gathering tool. Use the collected items to craft new and better equipment. Do you want to store them, sell for good money, or trade with other players? The choice is yours!\n\n{470492158655909}\n\nMANAGE AND UPGRADE YOUR EQUIPMENT\n\nGather a diverse range of weapons. Upgrade stats and customize them with elemental modifications. Beware of other players lurking on the planets for your loot. To avoid being left with nothing, store some of them in your storage room to be ready for your next expedition.\n\n{947075740229393}\n\nENTER THE UNKNOWN \n\nTake up the challenge and fight for the loot on the uncharted territories of unique planets, each brimming with diverse landscapes, challenging terrains, and protected bases full of precious items. Discover a wealth of resources, hunt, and engage in an intense fight against a multitude of enemies each presenting distinct challenges. \n\n{1551836102046006}", "short_description": "Become one of the Hunters in Astro Hunters VR - PvPvE extraction shooter set in space. Explore diverse planets, fight with different enemies, craft, gather resources, and upgrade your weapons. But remember there are also other hunters on the planet. Will you ally, fight, or betray - it's up to you!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.wenklystudio.com/privacy-policy-astro-hunters-vr", "developer_terms_of_servic